snippet.title: FOAMSTARS｜Release Date Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
#FOAMSTARS #PS5 #PS4
The new 4v4 foam party shooter
FOAMSTARS will release on February 6 2024!

What's more, FOAMSTARS slides into the PlayStation®Plus Monthly Games line-up at launch! 

All PlayStation®Plus members can download and keep FOAMSTARS on PS4™ and PS5™ at no extra cost between February 6, 2024 and March 4, 2024.

Let the bubbles fly!

▼Check out the latest FOAMSTARS information!
Official Site: https://foamstarsgame.com/
Instagram: https://instagram.com/foamstarsgame 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/FoamstarsGame
TikTok: www.tiktok.com/@foamstarsgame
